OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776251470
OL,3,CMoment thousands of pounds worth of
OL,4,Citems stolen from shop seized by police
OL,6,FThousands of pounds worth of items
OL,7,Fstolen from a shop in Worthing have
OL,8,Fbeen seized by police from a car.
OL,10,FSussex Police said officers were
OL,11,Falerted to a high-value theft from a
OL,12,FTesco store in Durrington at about
OL,13,F8.10am on Thursday 9 April.
OL,15,FSuspects entered the store and stole
OL,16,Fitems including electric toothbrushes,
OL,17,Fbaby monitors, and electric shavers.
OL,19,FLater that day, officers from the
OL,20,FSurrey Roads Policing Unit stopped a
OL,21,Fcar on the M25.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
