OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776251470
OL,3,CMoment thousands of pounds worth of
OL,4,Citems stolen from shop seized by police
OL,6,FThey found items linked to the theft
OL,7,Fin Worthing, alongside other suspected
OL,8,Fstolen items worth thousands of pounds
OL,9,Fin the vehicle.
OL,11,FTwo men aged 19 and 22 from Hemel
OL,12,FHempstead, Hertfordshire, were
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of shop theft
OL,14,Fand handling stolen goods.
OL,16,FThey have been bailed, pending further
OL,17,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
