OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776251470
OL,3,CMoment thousands of pounds worth of
OL,4,Citems stolen from shop seized by police
OL,6,FWorthing District Commander, James
OL,7,FDavidson, said: "We understand the
OL,8,Fpublic's concern about shop theft and
OL,9,Fthe impact it has on businesses and
OL,10,Ffor our community.
OL,12,F"This was a shocking and brazen
OL,13,Fattempt to take items from shops worth
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,16,F"The two suspects had used
OL,17,Fsophisticated means to steal the items
OL,18,Fand went to great lengths to evade
OL,19,Fbeing caught.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776251470
OL,3,CMoment thousands of pounds worth of
OL,4,Citems stolen from shop seized by police
OL,6,F"But the matter was reported to us and
OL,7,Fwe were able to trace a vehicle into
OL,8,FSurrey.
OL,10,F"Thanks to the excellent
OL,11,Fprofessionalism and teamwork from our
OL,12,FSurrey Police colleagues, both
OL,13,Fsuspects were safely detained and
OL,14,Fbrought back to custody in Sussex for
OL,15,Finterview.
OL,17,F"Tackling shoplifting is a priority
OL,18,Ffor us, and we have seen a significant
OL,19,Freduction in the number of incidents
OL,20,Fin Worthing in recent months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
