PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776251470
OL,3,CMoment thousands of pounds worth of
OL,4,Citems stolen from shop seized by police
OL,6,F"We are catching and prosecuting
OL,7,Fthieves and targeting the most
OL,8,Fprolific offenders through Operation
OL,9,FApprentice. It shows the determination
OL,10,Fand hard work of officers and our
OL,11,Fpartners to tackle crime and keep
OL,12,Fpeople safe in Worthing."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
